# Cloudflare Pages _redirects
# Routes short links through the Supabase 'go' edge function for click tracking.
# Pattern: /go/<slug> → Supabase /functions/v1/go?slug=<slug> (302, logs click, then redirects to intake)
# Status 302 (proxy) so the URL bar still shows /go/<slug> when fetched, but the response is the 302 from Supabase.

/go/:slug   https://vsbytdonbuwrrlmwteaw.supabase.co/functions/v1/go?slug=:slug   302
/go         https://tropesmith.com/?utm_source=go_unknown                          302


